-- MOVES-Blackstone hires Arteaga, Fernandez from Rothschild
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 11:50AM EDT
-- None



Sept 22 (Reuters) - Blackstone Group LP <BX.N> said it appointed Borja Arteaga as senior managing director to head its restructuring and M&A advisory in the Iberian Peninsula.

Arteaga joins from Rothschild where he was the co-head of Spanish operations. He has also worked at Goldman Sachs <GS.N> and Santander <SAN.MC>.